@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_copmgc(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = (wp.cos(wp.abs(tmp + 0.64)) * (v1 * 0.91))
    v0 = (wp.cos((tmp + 0.01 * v0 + 0.64)) - tmp)
    v1 = v1
    v0 = ((wp.cos(v1 + 0.10) - (v1 + 0.80 - tmp + 0.54)) / (0.78 * wp.abs(v0 + 0.61)))
    data[tid] = v0
